{"tid":198923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加媒為美斯喊冤：金球評委後悔吧！","createTime":"2017-04-12T22:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T00:41:28.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1f722f328193cfccddab572cf8cd00973571ca","tid":198923,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"加媒為美斯喊冤：金球評委後悔吧！<br />\n加媒為美斯喊冤：金球評委後悔吧！<br />\n瀏覽次數3.6k\t 回覆數量62<br />\n樓主<br />\n小寶寶999<br />\n2016-12-19 03:12 PM<br />\n#1<br />\n<a href=\"http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20161219/6690203/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F1%2F20161219%2F6690203%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=baba6434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20161219/6690203/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴塞主場4-1力克同城打比死敵愛斯賓奴，美斯此役的表現十分搶眼。巴塞隆拿當地媒體當然不會放過這個為自家球星造勢的機會。<br />\n比賽結束之後，加泰羅尼亞當地媒體《每日體育報》就發表評論文章，標題為：「美斯，以及金球獎評委們的懊悔」，該文先是回顧了美斯今場比賽的精彩發揮：2分鐘6次過人製造了蘇亞雷斯和阿爾巴的兩粒入球，之後自己又策動並攻入了一粒入球。<br />\n<br />\n該文寫道：「全世界共有173名記者參加了金球獎的評選，其中只有13人把美斯放在了他們選票中的第一位，絕大多數都把這個位置給了C.朗拿度。現在，他們會發現，自己選擇了商業化包裝下的球員，而沒有選擇世界上最好的足球運動員――現在以及一直以來最好的足球運動員。」<br />\n<br />\n該文最後寫道：「在製造兩粒入球並攻入一球後，美斯讓所有沒有選他的金球獎評委感到後悔。」<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿當地另外一家媒體《世界體育報》也不甘寂寞，該報發表文章，稱《法國足球》雜誌在Twitter上遭到球迷「轟炸」，金球獎的評選正是該雜誌組織的。在世體的文章中可以看到，不少球迷都在自己的Twitter瘋狂@上《法國足球》的官方帳號，球迷的Twitter內容諸如：「趕緊重新組織投票吧」、「把美斯明年的金球獎先準備好」&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"354147cf56341690a617aeb04480fd116c843b85","tid":198923,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114dccd917c856120f9fd539179bcb762a691f2c","tid":198923,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:22:57.000Z","msg":"估唔到牙朗三十歲後可以追貼金球獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年唔覺意又拎多個就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31960dcfcbb957b32b278c44fb05f9ba6c4c44d","tid":198923,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後悔啲咩？冇放小花去第三？"},{"pid":"801bf765e79a89159df81b1da4a65ba5f75eef30","tid":198923,"uid":24925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"真新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de93116bd1643eb14617ea50b67a57653ac01eaf","tid":198923,"uid":30808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:05:56.000Z","msg":"用愛斯賓奴嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d96346bb462d9f324df595161366b37b43a3bfd","tid":198923,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"即係球員踢一場好波 就即時係金球獎得主 咁都幾多候選人"},{"pid":"44a1e9b9e4d2eeae5f8772045675ea5e16f1304f","tid":198923,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩<br />\n快d脫離西班牙<br />\n<br />\n為呢個世界添多d火種好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da586b1c890d403e0912a4868acf9cb3f5c514d9","tid":198923,"uid":53543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用愛斯賓奴嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打吡喎"},{"pid":"155c34d4597f0c2ecf1ad684daa8c38bc4a1ad8f","tid":198923,"uid":99911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"C朗嚟緊今年攞金球？咪笑死人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係攞都係做馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff5bd87db02868edb1b1dcaee917dfa9be0b400","tid":198923,"uid":92736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用愛斯賓奴嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/